-- Mexico’s Cayo Arcas, Dos Bocas, Coatzacoalcos Closed: Ministry
-- B y   B e n   B a i n
-- 2013-11-03T17:24:02Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-11-03/mexico-s-cayo-arcas-dos-bocas-coatzacoalcos-closed-ministry.html
Petroleos Mexicanos’s crude export
terminals in  Dos Bocas , Coatzacoalcos and Cayo Arcas were closed
today because of adverse weather conditions, according to the
Mexico Merchant Marine.  The agency, part of the Communications and Transport
Ministry, announced the closures in  its daily weather bulletin .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ben Bain in Mexico City at 
 bbain2@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Sylvia Wier at 
 swier@bloomberg.net  